ype":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>A <strong>100% personalized<\/strong> therapy session that targets <em>your <\/em>specific needs + <strong>extended velcro straps<\/strong> designed to fit any leg size <strong>comfortably<\/strong>.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["heading_JreAfY","text_m4TEhk"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Untitled_design.gif","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"text_first","image_behavior":"none","content_layout":"no-overlap","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left","section_color_scheme":"","color_scheme":"","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"image_with_text_dVK7bT":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_qE8eXF":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Why You'll LOVE IT","heading_size":"h2"}},"text_YgtX9x":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><strong>3 Heating Levels: <\/strong>Gentle warmth to deep, intense heat.<br\/><strong>3 Vibration Modes: <\/strong>Choose between constant soothing or pulsing massage.<br\/><strong>Laser & Red Light: <\/strong>Can be toggled on or off independently.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["heading_qE8eXF","text_YgtX9x"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Screenshot_2025-12-13_172711.png","height":"small","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","image_behavior":"none","content_layout":"no-overlap","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left","section_color_scheme":"","color_scheme":"","padding_top":8,"padding_bottom":8}},"image_with_text_66MeqQ":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_TUfTB8":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>One device Endless possibilities<\/strong>","heading_size":"h2"}},"text_TpAdQ8":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>The design fits perfectly on your 💪 <strong>Shoulders, <\/strong>🦾 <strong>Elbows, and<\/strong>🦶 <strong>Heels.<br\/><br\/>DON'T WAIT!<\/strong><br\/>Prevent serious injuries and surgeries before they begin.<\/p><p><strong>FREE THE KNEES<\/strong><br\/>Reduce pain, stiffness, swelling and stress build up over time.<\/p><p><strong>GET MOBILITY BACK!<\/strong><br\/>Move freely, being able resume your daily activities comfortably.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["heading_TUfTB8","text_TpAdQ8"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/1_1.webp","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"small","layout":"text_first","image_behavior":"none","content_layout":"no-overlap","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"center","mobile_content_alignment":"left","section_color_scheme":"","color_scheme":"","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"rich_text_ggHFyt":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_jxQBtL":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h1><strong>WHAT OUR CUSTOMERS SAY<\/strong><\/h1>"}}},"block_order":["text_jxQBtL"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"scheme-5914609d-643e-4c60-9316-611a49b3c419","full_width":true,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"rich_text_RAhLX8":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_gai4Uy":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"\"This thing is amazing.\"","heading_size":"h2"}},"text_pM69x7":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>\"I have been a dance teacher for many years and<strong> my knees are definitely not what they used to be<\/strong>. This Knee massager is <strong>fantastic and not only provides relief during the process but also increases mobility after the fact. 10 mins on each knee once a day and I already notice a difference. Well worth it\"<\/strong><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_gai4Uy","text_pM69x7"],"disabled":true,"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"scheme-156b13b9-b85d-4aea-b2d5-bc69b8208eff","full_width":true,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"rich_text_aHrm9n":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_iF9cgM":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Do You Relate?","heading_size":"h1"}},"text_GJETWy":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Imagine being able to<strong> relieve your chronic pains, stiffness, swelling<\/strong> <strong>from <\/strong>the comfort of <strong>your home – in just a few minutes<\/strong> – <strong>without <\/strong>taking <strong>painkillers<\/strong> or <strong>expensive  lengthy therapy<\/strong>…<br\/><br\/><strong>There is so much more out there in life<\/strong>, however it requires mobility, no one wants to carry one another. Everyone wants to enjoy the beauty of life and its special moments. It requires moving, <strong>having somthing in which prevents the moving is a big problem.<\/strong><br\/><br\/>Premium Heals isn't just a store for your health, its a team that solved the problem, from what started as issues in all our families to trying everything from A-Z, surgeries, therapy, medication, and so much more. <strong>We lost some important people in our lives. We don't want that for you and your loved ones.<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>It took a while until we found the solutions, trial after trial. Product researches, doctors and so much time. We finally found somthing...<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>For the first time in moderation, your able to heal your problems from the good of your home without the need of<\/strong> taking drugs, spending time for therapy that would throw you if you didn't pay and surgeries that simply put you out for as long as its needed. <br\/><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_iF9cgM","text_GJETWy"],"disabled":true,"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"scheme-156b13b9-b85d-4aea-b2d5-bc69b8208eff","full_width":true,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":52}},"image_with_text_zAQdCQ":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_JiXcGN":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>\"This is one of the best things I’ve bought in a long time.\"<\/strong>","heading_size":"h2"}},"text_MFJ6EF":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>I'm a sixty one year old carpenter\/building contractor , <strong>knees are bone on bone, left one became so stiff couldn't bend it , have been waiting for knee replacement for two years<\/strong>, I received the Ultra Knee Massager and used on each knee for the auto timed <strong>10 minutes, saw results immediately<\/strong>, been using for a week now and have <strong>had three friends with knee problems try mine and all three have noticed some relief after only 1 minutes and have all ordered one. relief is absolutely amazing.<\/strong><\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["heading_JiXcGN","text_MFJ6EF"],"disabled":true,"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2_2080cbb0-505a-486a-8604-9424f482b460.webp","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","image_behavior":"none","content_layout":"no-overlap","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left","section_color_scheme":"","color_scheme":"","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"image_banner_dkqwzt":{"type":"image-banner","blocks":{"buttons_bC8MHF":{"type":"buttons","settings":{"button_label_1":"GET IT","button_link_1":"shopify:\/\/products\/ultra-knee-massager","button_style_secondary_1":false,"button_label_2":"","button_link_2":"shopify:\/\/products\/ultra-knee-massager","button_style_secondary_2":false}}},"block_order":["buttons_bC8MHF"],"disabled":true,"name":"t:sections.image-banner.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Screenshot_2025-12-07_175328.png","image_overlay_opacity":0,"image_height":"adapt","image_behavior":"none","d